**Lion and the Mouse**

Once there was a little mouse who lived in a big jungle. One day he was wandering alone when he saw the lion sleeping under a 
tree. He was unaware of how dangerous the lion was. He started jumping over the lion. Soon enough, the lion woke up.
He held the little mouse in his giant paw and was just about to gobble him up but he was startled by the mouse's squeaks
 